Men's and Women's
Fitness, Exercise and Workout Clothing

 





























Proper Workout and Exercise Clothing 
are just as important as Weightlifting Belts and 
Weightlifting 
Gloves. The clothing that you workout in, should be slightly lose 
fitting and comfortable on your body, as opposed to very tight 
fitting. This is important, because it ensures that your clothing 
will not hamper your circulation. It is very important to have 
proper circulation when you are exercising as blood and oxygen are 
trying to get to your muscles and toxins are trying to be removed. 
Your Workout Clothing should allow for a full range of motion and 
not restrict your movement in any way. Baseball Caps are also a 
great piece of gear for working out. A baseball cap will help keep 
the sweat and hair out of your eyes during your workout routine.
 
















 
 

 
 
 
 


 
















