IVANKO RM-EPC Machined Plates, Machined Chromed End 
Plate Dumbbells

All of our fixed weight 
dumbbells incorporate Ivanko's 
PermaLock fastening system which 
employs proprietary machining tolerances 
and surface preparation to achieve a 
metal-to-metal bond that requires 400 
foot pounds of torque to twist apart. 
That's the power of a V8 engine.










 
 
 

 





































 
 
 

 



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 
 



 




 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 



 
 
 

 


 
 
 

 




















